column5: Heeeey.... Evening, can ya do a project for tonight??
Uum, It's quite late and I was going to sle-
I will pay you a bunch if you do it tonight :)
Sure! :3
Yohoo! Let's get this project started
I am so excited!
Thank you fot accepting the comission
No! I told you I don't want it like this
I am sorry, how do you want it then?
You should know how I wanted it before I explained to you so many times already!
Look it's really late and I am tired, but I will try to deliver the wor-
Well, it's clear that you're not ready for this! What? You think you're some kind artist because you do commissions on Twitter!?
I need a moment
A twelve-year-old boy draws better than you
It's overpriced if you are only delivering this
Irregular shapes, inconsistent lines, it looks like a scribble
Did you draw it with the mouse?
Your art is not worth it
You made a mistake by becoming independent so soon...
Your parents must be ashamed of you...
You will never achieve anything in life
You've wasted your life on this...
You.Are.Nothing...
Heeeeey.... Great job! I never doubted you :)
